  <div class="ct">
  
<p>I know it wouldn't be easy, but you have such a wonderful platform at Daily Kos and your other outlets that gives you a head start over most other people when it comes to getting the word out and marketing any book you write.</p>
<p>Even if you don't find a publisher, there's always the Amazon Kindle store, Createspace, and other self-publishing venues to consider.</p>

